<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink378">
<l>celliya muyalip pāaya ciṟakar</l>
<l>vāva lukakku mālaiyām pulampap</l>
<l>pōkiya vavaṭkō nōvēṉ ṟēmoḻit</l>
<l>tuṇaiyilaḷ kaliḻu neñci</l>
<l>ṉiṇaiyē ruṇka ṇivaṭkunō vatuvē</l>
      </lg>
     <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>I grieve for that girl, </l>
<l>who left [me] to be lonely in the evening times, </l>
<l>when bats soar upward, with their spread wings, attempting to fly. </l>
<l>And grieving is also for this girl</l> 
<l>with a pair of beautiful kohl eyes,</l>
<l>whose heart is in pain without a sweet-voiced friend.  </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
